</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-sans text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark antialiased transition-colors duration-200">
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto min-h-screen relative pb-20">
        <header class="pt-8 pb-6 px-5 sticky top-0 bg-background-light/90 dark:bg-background-dark/90 backdrop-blur-md z-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        Deneyim
                    </h1>
                    <button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/30 transition-all active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-xl">add</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark font-medium">
                    Kariyer yolculuğunu buradan düzenle.
                </p>
            </div>
            <button class="w-full mt-6 bg-primary text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:scale-[0.98] transition-transform">
                <span class="material-icons-round">add_circle_outline</span>
                Yeni Deneyim Ekle
            </button>
        </header>
        <main class="px-5 space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-icons-round text-2xl">code</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Junior .NET Developer</h2>
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark">Acunmedya Akademi</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 py-1 px-2 rounded-lg whitespace-nowrap">
                        Kasım 2024 - Haz 2025
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
                    .NET Core ve MVC alanlarında projeler geliştirdim. Backend mimarisi üzerine çalıştım.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 pt-4">
                    <button class="flex-1 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:bg-gray-200">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-base">edit</span>
                        Düzenle
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex-1 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 hover:bg-red-100 dark:hover:bg-red-900/30 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:bg-red-200">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-base">delete</span>
                        Sil
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-500 shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-icons-round text-2xl">work_outline</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Proje Yönetimi Stajyeri</h2>
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark">Sca Social</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 py-1 px-2 rounded-lg whitespace-nowrap">
                        Eylül 2025 - Kasım 2025
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
                    Yönetim organizasyon, bilişim hukuku, veri bilimi ve proje yönetimi gibi konularda eğitim aldım.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 pt-4">
                    <button class="flex-1 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:bg-gray-200">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-base">edit</span>
                        Düzenle
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex-1 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 hover:bg-red-100 dark:hover:bg-red-900/30 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:bg-red-200">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-base">delete</span>
                        Sil
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-900/20 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-500 shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-icons-round text-2xl">monitor</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Junior .NET Developer</h2>
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark">AkademiQ AI School</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 py-1 px-2 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-1 whitespace-nowrap">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                        Devam Ediyor
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
                    .NET Core alanında projeler geliştiriyorum. Yapay zeka entegrasyonları üzerine çalışmalar yapıyorum.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 pt-4">
                    <button class="flex-1 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:bg-gray-200">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-base">edit</span>
                        Düzenle
                    </button>
                    <button class="flex-1 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 hover:bg-red-100 dark:hover:bg-red-900/30 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:bg-red-200">
                        <span class="material-icons-round text-base">delete</span>
                        Sil
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 transition-colors opacity-60">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-500 shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-icons-round text-2xl">school</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold leading-tight">Stajyer</h2>
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-sub-light dark:text-text-sub-dark">Tech Startup</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 pt-4 mt-4">
                    <div class="h-8 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded w-full"></div>
                    <div class="h-8 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded w-full"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        
    </div>
    <script>
        // Simple script to toggle dark mode for demo purposes if clicked on title
        document.querySelector('h1').addEventListener('click', () => {
            document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark');
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>